00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:48,840
But, you know, I mean, just some questionable things.

255
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:49,460
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

256
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:50,320
Never talked about.

257
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:50,700
Yeah.

